  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to describe current treatment practices in the US for managing acute
      uncomplicated diverticulitis. In addition, we will identify clinical factors associated with
      the decision to discharge versus hospitalize patients with uncomplicated diverticulitis with
      the goal of informing clinical decision-making and providing a foundation for diagnostic
      algorithms to guide clinical practice.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
